reviews.review_text: binge factor Jack Straw>Deal,Truckin' and JBG rip.
Nice! Great Estimated-Eyes on this one, very spirited playing by Garcia, solid soundboard, from the underrated November 78 tour.

He packs a 45 Stagger Lee may be audience but it is good quality aud.
Great placement for this tune.
ESTIMATED-this tune with Donna > Eyes (77-78)
you just can't top that. (13 minutes plus on both tunes here)
Sweet jam into drums
and very mellow build-up to the NFA
TRUCKIN' as Set 2 closer is so obvious a choice
but so rarely explored over the years.
This is a good show with many minor lyric flubs
 Maybe NOT the best choice with headphones
because of the different sound textures 
of the varied recording sources
